hat in a few years the company might be getting involved in virtual reality products according to quartz and the new york times systrom and krieger implemented a system to overcome bottlenecks and slow decisionmaking in the company by scheduling meetings in which only decisions are taken this approach was informed by systroms interest in academic business theories in particular clayton m christensens concept of the â€œthe innovatorâ€™s dilemmaâ€ views on copying ideas in the industryedit instagram has been called out in multiple occasions for copying various new functions from its closest competitor snapchat regarding the issue systrom argued that all new services launched by tech companies nowadays are remixes of existing products and that all of these ideas are original when you remix them and bring your own flavour forbes listedit in  systrom was listed in the forbes  under  list under the socialmobile category in  the magazine ranked systrom as a billionaire with an estimated net worth of  billion the fortune came about as a result of facebook stocks rising more than  personal lifeedit according to the guardian systrom enjoys fine food golf skiing and holidays at californiaâ€™s lake tahoeÂ  in february  systrom met with pope francis at the vatican where they discussed the power of images in uniting people across borders cultures and generations referencesedit  katherine rushton  whos getting rich from facebooks bn instagram deal the telegraphÂ   leadership walmartÂ   a b how old is kevin systrom quora  retrieved on   a b c d kiss jemima  instagram ceo kevin systrom were working on time travel the guardian issnÂ  retrieved Â   holliston native strikes it rich with smartphone app instagram  framingham ma the metrowest daily news  retrieved on   elizabeth v pels  northjerseycom retrieved  october Â   elizabeth v pels  northjerseycomÂ   albert pels obituary  peterborough nh  monadnock ledgertranscript monadnock ledgertranscriptÂ   redefining the culture and the indu